anda]], Angola || {{fb|ANG}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 3\u20130 || [[2015 Africa Cup of Nations qualification Group C|2015 Africa Cup of Nations qualification]]\n|-\n| 12. || 10 January 2015 || rowspan=2 | Mbombela Stadium, Nelspruit, South Africa  || {{fb|SWZ|name=Swaziland}} || align=center | '''5'''\u20131 || align=center | 5\u20131 || rowspan=2| Friendly\n|-\n| 13. || 13 January 2015 || {{fb|BOT}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20130 || align=center | 2\u20130 \n|-\n| 14. || 25 January 2015 || [[Nuevo Estadio de Ebebiy\u00edn]], [[Ebebiy\u00edn]], [[Equatorial Guinea]] || {{fb|CGO}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20131 || align=center | 1\u20132 || [[2015 Africa Cup of Nations Group A|2015 Africa Cup of Nations]]\n|-\n| 15. || 6 June 2015 || [[Stade Yves-du-Manoir]], Paris, France || {{fb|CMR}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20131 || align=center | 2\u20133 || Friendly\n|-\n| 16. || 13 June 2015 || Stade du 4 Ao\u00fbt, Ouagadougou, Burkina Faso || {{fb|COM}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 2\u20130 || [[2017 Africa Cup of Nations qualification Group D|2017 Africa Cup of Nations qualification]]\n|-\n| 17. || 19 October 2015 || [[Stade de l'Aube]], [[Troyes]], France || {{fb|MLI}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20132 || align=center | 1\u20134 || Friendly\n|-\n| 18. || 28 January 2017 || [[Stade d'Angondj\u00e9]], [[Libreville]], Gabon || {{fb|TUN}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 2\u20130 || rowspan=2| [[2017 Africa Cup of Nations knockout stage|2017 Africa Cup of Nations]]\n|-\n| 19. || 1 February 2017 || [[Stade de l'Amiti\u00e9]], Libreville, Gabon || {{fb|EGY}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20131 || align=center | 1\u20131 \n|-\n| 20. || rowspan=\"2\" | 10 June 2017 || rowspan=\"2\" | Stade du 4 Ao\u00fbt, Ouagadougou, Burkina Faso || rowspan=\"2\" | {{fb|ANG}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"| 3\u20131 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[2019 Africa Cup of Nations qualification Group 